{
  "texts": [
    "A DRP is considered correctly identi ed if the response mentions the speci c medication name and provides a recommendation to perform an action or intervention to change or amend the medication order.",
    "If only the drug class is mentioned; or no action is suggested, the DRP is not considered accurately identi ed.",
    "The concordance of co-pilot and autonomous mode with human expert as benchmark was measured using accuracy, precision, recall, and F1 score as per a previous published study.",
    "33 Accuracy is expressed as a percentage of correctly identi ed DRP against expert.",
    "Precision, which denotes the fraction of DRPs correctly identi ed amongst all suggested DRPs, was de ned as precision = true positives / (true positives + false positives)."
  ]
}